&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Talent Sourcing:&lt;/strong&gt; Proactively identify and engage top talent for technical and non-technical roles through job boards, social media, referrals, and networking events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full-Cycle Recruiting:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage the entire recruitment process, from job postings and resume screenings to interviewing, negotiating offers, and onboarding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employer Branding:&lt;/strong&gt; Help craft and communicate the startup’s brand to attract top-tier candidates, emphasizing the company&#39;s culture, mission, and growth opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
