&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive in a fast-paced, evolving environment with changing hiring needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are an excellent communicator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You think outside the box to find creative solutions to hiring challenges, especially in competitive job markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive when you truly own something&lt;/li&gt;
